-- Gambino Crime Family Associate Scarpaci Pleads Guilty in Racketeering Case
-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 2010-12-30T16:50:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-30/gambino-crime-family-associate-scarpaci-pleads-guilty-in-racketeering-case.html
Gambino crime family associate Michael
Scarpaci in New York pleaded guilty to a charge of racketeering 
enterprise today in Manhattan federal court, and faces a maximum 
sentence of 20 years in prison.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bob Van Voris in New York at 
 rvanvoris@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
